                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-165" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS AUSTIN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. The prosecutor gave me informa<lb></lb>tion, and I was looking for the prisoner until the 13th of November, when I apprehended him at his father's house.</p>
